title: #92Noon! Zimm/Utecht/Leber/Korzo/Marney
description: Vikings Atopics and trashtalk out of the gate with Cowboys fan Jamar from Brooklyn Park...hear Mike Zimmer's X's & O's chat with PA...former Gopher/SB winning TE Ben Utecht...Leber in studio midway through...Korzo follows him during final hour...Marney Gellner with a cameo to wrap the show!
